Citation.sTitle: Vapor Liquid Equilibrium of N-Formylmorpholine with Toluene and Xylene at 101.33 kPa
Citation.sAbstract: Isobaric vapor liquid equilibrium (VLE) data for toluene + NFM, o-xylene + NFM, m-xylene + NFM, and p-xylene + NFM were measured at 101.33 kPa with a modified Rose-Williams still. Wilson and NRTL equations were used to correlate the VLE data through a nonlinear least-squares method.
